  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Local Cooperation Fund (LCF) in Vietnam</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This community-based climate change adaptation project will provide scientific basis and understanding of the local perception of and adaption capacity to climate changes through case studies/researches in selected sites in one of the most highly vulnerable areas to climate changes in Vietnam - Thua Thien Hue province. This project is unique in term of linking local issues and actions to policy development at local, provincial and national levels. Furthermore, the project would be developed as IREB/International Programme on Climate Change and Risk Variability-IPCRV&#xE2;&#x80;&#x99;s demo-site research for climate change, where many Vietnamese and international institutions/scientists will be involved in future.</narrative>
  </description>
